page_title: What's new in Azure OpenAI Service?
page_description: Learn about the latest news and features updates for Azure OpenAI.
chunk_content: February 2023### New Features- .NET SDK(inference) preview release | Samples- Terraform SDK update to support Azure OpenAI management operations.- Inserting text at the end of a completion is now supported with the `suffix` parameter.### Updates- Content filtering is on by default.New articles on:- Monitoring an Azure OpenAI Service- Plan and manage costs for Azure OpenAINew training course:- Intro to Azure OpenAI
